---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import eoh_png from '../../assets/images/eoh.png';
---

<section 
    id="landing_page" 
    data-color="var(--color-blue)" 
    class="color-section h-[calc(100vh-var(--nav-height))] w-full snap-start flex flex-row items-end overflow-hidden shrink-0"
    style="scroll-margin-top: var(--nav-height);"
>
    <div class="w-[65vw] h-auto flex items-end leading-0">
        <img 
            src={eoh_png.src}
            alt="Eis o Homem - Still"
            class="w-full h-auto block m-0 align-bottom"
        />
    </div>

    <div class="w-[35vw] pr-[3.5vw] pb-[10vh] pl-5">
        <div class="flex flex-col mb-6">
            <span class="block text-base md:text-lg">
                Coming Soon
            </span>
            <span class="block text-base md:text-lg font-bold -mt-1">
                Behold the Man
            </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs">
            As a teenager I learned that desire can also be a wound. I aim to capture that instant: when the body learns devotion and dread in the same breath.
            <br/>
            Adolescence arrives as the body awakens, a founding moment when desire can be an experience of the sacred, or an omen of death. The film observes that threshold, giving it a place and form.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>